import React from 'react'
import { Container, Row, Col } from 'react-bootstrap';
import Form from 'react-bootstrap/Form';
import InputGroup from 'react-bootstrap/InputGroup';
const Home = () => {
    return (
        <Container className='mt-5 pt-5' style={{ width: 1100 }}>
             <InputGroup className="mb-3">
                        <Form.Control
                            placeholder="Search Here" />
                        <InputGroup.Text >Search</InputGroup.Text>
                    </InputGroup>
            <Row>
                <Col sm={6}>
                    <InputGroup className="mb-3">
                        <Form.Control
                            placeholder="Title " />
                        <InputGroup.Text >Add</InputGroup.Text>
                    </InputGroup>
                </Col>
                <Col sm={6}>
                    <InputGroup className="mb-3">
                    <textarea class="form-control" rows="5" placeholder="Description" name="message" required ></textarea>
                    </InputGroup>
                </Col>
            </Row>
        </Container>
    )
}

export default Home
